\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 When you came back from South Africa did you carry on with office work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Yes. Yes. Yes, I came back from South Africa. I was - a year out of work, and o
f course I had no - Social Security then because of course I hadn't been in England for so many years. But - eventually I got a job with - the Automobile Association as a matter of fact. As a foreign touring expert because I was the only one that knew any
t
hing about Africa in the staff. And afterwards, I became assistant to the foreign secretary of the - Automobile Association, because I was there - I then carried on that - through the war, I wasn't called up for the last war - until - oh - in the 19 - lat
e
 1950's, when I gave up the job and took a smaller job to - because of various other things, and - carried on with the job then which - of compiling - information concerning touring all over the world really, I was - which was my job right the whole way t
hrough. So that I've always been in - clerical - clerical work you see. Right from - boyhood as you might say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Could you tell me how old your parents were when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Oh - oh dear, this is - I should say in the - about forty I should think. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7673867\charrsid15017164 
Thirty to forty. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 
Because - see - mother died in 1965 - no, no, 19 - 1956. She was then eighty-five. Well that's - getting her back to - 1900 would be - would be fifty-six - yes, it was about - the forty - because of course you see, they'd both been - wh
at shall I say - both being in service for a long while or working, father had beer in the Army and that sort of thing and - they were rather late - well as a matter of fact, quite a lot of people were rather late in life in - I mean, my uncles - my uncle
s were all - in the thirties - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7673867\charrsid15017164 forties}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 
 - before they - before they got married. Because of course it was a case of - well you had to have the sort of - some money behind you, and money was - difficult to get hold of sort of thing, that was the - that was the whole trouble.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
