Well I had two sisters, both younger than I. Let's see, there's only one left - living now and she's about sixty-two, so she was born - '71, she was born about 1908. Or so. The other o
ne died some years ago. But I know it was my job when I was a schoolboy at times to have to take them out in the pram. Thing I used to hate. We always had arguments when we grew up as to - I never took them out. But -
