 had on was a - a sort of night gown and we had a lovely snow battle until I was discovered and there was a shindy. I - I - but - it - it had no - no ill effects, that's the funny part about it, in fact I - it cured the measles. But actually - the main th
ing I dean remember of those, except of course Christmastimes when we used to join together for - for - sort of festivities, we were usually on our own but of course we used to have to make - make our own then. We had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid920634\charrsid15017164 to press}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164  the button or switch on or anything of that sort.
