No, we - we cooked in the - they both - both the wives luckily got on very well together, cooked both in the same kitchen. I think there were two gas stoves, but I won't be sure of
 that. But it was really a sharing of the house, the only thing is we - we didn't live in one another's laps, if you can understand what I mean.
