 they ate their - their meals in their rooms and we ate our meals in our room you see. It was a - let me see - there were three rooms and a scullery downstairs, and - three rooms upstairs. So we divided them up that way you see. Yes. They - were then were
 there - oh - for some years really. I suppose I was about ten or eleven when we left there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 The other would have been away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 No, no, he - he retired from the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7673867\charrsid15017164 navy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
