Not then, no, in the last house there was. Because I was away from home and there was spare room and - mother did have - people in then. Mostly single people who she used to - cater for. But that was only - after - oh -
 there were some I think before - no, there weren't any before - any before 1914, it was after the last war really that she started to do that. Because of course father was out of the Arsenal then, he was - discovered to be redundant - before there was su
