nd she placed a plate of - dinner before you, you - well you just about saw the edge of the plate, as you can testify. And consequently I don't - I'm almost sure she didn't make any great - any great profit out of it. But - while we were children there we
re - never - oh there was occasionally - now and again we'd have somebody in perhaps to - meet some - sort of - emergency. We'd take somebody in for a little while.
