Yes, they were. They were actually self contained, you see, I mean - their - well they used to have their newspaper of course, although - practically every - usually u
sed to be either the local newspaper, or else a Sunday newspaper, there was never - very seldom newspapers in the week. They used to - have their amusements, and we used to join in, such as the local flower show, which the high day and - everything else o
f
 the - the village in the summer, when you had sports and - everybody produced their best marrow and - all the other things. And we youngsters - I say we youngsters now calling myself one of the village - we used to be classes for us for - the best bunch 
