\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Oh yes, all round - religious - religious - Salvation Army and everybody else. They'd all be going hammer and tong
s. On Sunday evenings. Sometimes you'd get it in the - in the week. You can perhaps get a midweek meeting. The I.L.P. or the - Socialist party and - oh all sorts of people used to - in fact - that carried on until - late in the thirties - forties.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 And you went along yourself?
