And afterwards - yes, as a boy. Although I was - perhaps not with my father - I used to go down and stand round listening to them. Oh yes, often - often used to do that. It was one of the things to do on a Sunday evening, if
 there was nothing else on you see, because - I mean, in those days there weren't any pictures and that sort of thing, you couldn't go to the cinema. There was only church or - or church or politics.
