nd - she was - I think the only way they showed the - disapproval was they just ostracized her, just wouldn't speak and all that sort of thing, that was the only - that's the only thing I can remember. That happened I know, as - once. Of course, in all - 
m
ilitary - garrison towns you always get the - local obliging lady, and she was one of those, and I think - well the - there was no proof of it but it was always suspected. And of course - although - it wasn't discussed in front of us children - we got to 
