 who'd had a - a gin or two too many - would - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342617\charrsid15017164 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 n argument would suddenly }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
