 strict on seeing we did that. I know I used to very often try and dodge it, I often used to leave it 'til next morning and perhaps do it while I was trying to have breakfast, and hear the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14378793\charrsid15017164 
