\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Oh they were - they were jolly good, I - I used to get on quite well with them.
 I had no trouble with them. They were quite characters, I remember one, a man named Lucas, he was usually named - he was usually called by us Pongo. I shall never forget that man one day, he - we had a young Indian in the class. Was a boy who - been }{
