\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 And they caned you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 
Oh yes, you got - you got a sixer on the hands. Sometimes you even got a rap over the knuckles with the edge of a ruler. A wooden ruler. If - you were writing and sort of didn't do it - weren't holding your pen properly or somethin
g of that sort. For real - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14378793\charrsid15017164 misdemeanors}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 
 you - usually got six - or four or three on the hands and - sometimes it was a case of - being marched out and - having to bend over and get six on the - the backside. I mean they were beastly painful at the time but
 I don't think they did us any harm. And I think it's one of the - the things they ought to - never should have done away with in the school at the present time. I think it would have - it would be - what shall I say - instill a little more discipline int
o - into things really. I mean it did not - it didn't do us any harm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Were the teachers particular about manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Yes. Oh yes, you had to - speak properly and - you know, please sir, yes sir and that sort of thing. Oh yes, they were very - very k
een about that. And about dress as far as that goes. Oh yes, you had to be neat - and tidy. And clean as far as that goes.
