\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 There was the cashier, how many others were there there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 
Oh well there was another clerk in the - in the office. But then there were various - salesmen used to use desks in the office. Specially if they were writing up any - any account or doing what they called their own spiv account. You 
see, in the trade at that time there was certain - lines of furniture, articles of furniture which were perhaps hanging fire, you put - you know, didn't sell very well. Well - if that was so the - the - the boss used to sort of put a spiv on and all - spi
