\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12126379 CV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 
Oh yes. He was always about the - about the - shop. He was name - well it was a company that the shop belonged to. He was the managing director, a man named Cannock. Oh yes, I - we - he was always about the place, 
of course one was always rather circumspect when he was about. But - he was quite fair and - would speak to one and that sort of thing, but - of course was rather - he had his private office upstairs, rather big room. And - was rather - sort of - up there
 sort of thing and one didn't one scuttled round when he was about and when he - when he'd gone you - resumed your normal pace sort of thing. He used to act as salesman as well at times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13179849 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792229\charrsid15017164 Were there quire a lot of slang words used in the shop?
